'''''Blood Sacrifice''''' was the personal [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]] of [[Warmaster]] [[Tsavong Lah]] during the [[Battle of Ebaq]]. Carrying a [[yammosk]], the vessel was also the flagship of the [[Battle Group of Yun-Yuuzhan]]. When the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] warmaster ordered an occupation of [[Ebaq 9]], ''Blood Sacrifice'' landed on the [[Moon/Legends|moon's]] surface. The vessel was destroyed shortly after leaving the surface when Lah ordered it back into space to rejoin and reinforce the Battle Group of Yun-Yuuzhan.

